T.query: select e.emp_no as e_emp_no, t.emp_no as t_emp_no, s.from_date, t.title from employees e join salaries s on e.emp_no = s.emp_no join titles t on e.emp_no = t.emp_no and t.from_date = s.from_date  where e.emp_no > 231013
